meditation actually leads to better health.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.000
And, so what you feel when you meditate,

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:32.500
you feel an overwhelming calmness

00:02:32.500 --> 00:02:38.500
and this is a calmness which goes
much more beyond normal relaxation.

00:02:38.500 --> 00:02:43.800
Because when you relax, 
you relax the body and if you lie on the sofa, 

00:02:43.800 --> 00:02:47.640
you may be relaxed, but if you worry about the future
you are not really relaxed. 

00:02:47.640 --> 00:02:51.820
So, when you're thoughtless,
you don't just relax the body, 

00:02:51.820 --> 00:02:56.620
you also relax the mind and your brain
and you cannot do it with any other way. 

00:02:56.620 --> 00:02:58.400
You can only do it by stopping to think.

00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:02.220
Stopping to worry about the future,
stopping to rumenate about the past 

00:03:02.220 --> 00:03:04.120
and be in the present.

00:03:04.500 --> 00:03:09.100
So, this overwhelming feeling
of peace within, calmness, 

00:03:09.100 --> 00:03:13.420
is associated with stress relief
and I'll show you later how.

00:03:13.420 --> 00:03:18.340
When you are mentally silent,
you have a better mental balance.

00:03:18.340 --> 00:03:22.300
And this is - because if you think
about it - all mental disorders

00:03:22.300 --> 00:03:25.680
are actually characterised by thought
problems.  

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:28.100
If you have schizophrenia
you have paranoid thoughts. 

00:03:28.100 --> 00:03:30.740
If you are obsessive-compulsive
you have obsessive thoughts.

00:03:30.740 --> 00:03:34.320
If you are ADHD you have racing
thoughts and if you are depressed

00:03:34.320 --> 00:03:38.480
you have negative thoughts which you ruminate about.

00:03:38.480 --> 00:03:44.660
So, it has also been shown that all disorders,
all mental disorders they have more mental clutter.  

00:03:44.660 --> 00:03:46.700
This has been shown over recent years.

00:03:46.700 --> 00:03:50.960
And meditation of course is
the reduction of the mental clutter.

00:03:50.960 --> 00:03:56.060
Because that's what it is, you stop
your thinking so you have less mental clutter.

00:03:56.060 --> 00:03:59.960
So therefore, mental silence is a state
of super mental balance.

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:04.880
More than normal people have, because
if you meditate and you have less mental

00:04:04.880 --> 00:04:09.100
clutter than a normal person, then
you are super healthy, and super balanced mentally.

00:04:09.194 --> 00:04:15.354
When you don't have any thoughts, you are much
more concentrated and you are much 

00:04:15.354 --> 00:04:20.534
more alert because your are pure consciousness without the content, which are the thoughts and the emotions.

00:04:20.534 --> 00:04:24.134
And if you go through life, the whole day you
throw out your thoughts and your 

00:04:24.134 --> 00:04:28.214
emotions into the world and you don't
really see reality as it really is.

00:04:28.320 --> 00:04:33.000
Because you constantly have the intermediation
of your thoughts and your emotions.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:39.080
So, when you have no thoughts -
you absorb reality as it really is.

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:43.440
So for example, if you're now listening to me you may
be thinking about the dinner later

00:04:43.440 --> 00:04:47.100
