in order to actually listen or attend.

00:04:47.100 --> 00:04:51.100
If you have no thoughts,
you absorb information much quicker.

00:04:51.100 --> 00:04:55.780
And it has been shown that children who meditate
have better attention at school,

00:04:55.780 --> 00:04:59.400
Zen Buddhists who have meditated for a long time
have better attention and

00:04:59.400 --> 00:05:04.700
