00:05:48.480 --> 00:05:51.760
you achieve a state
of emotional detachment.

00:05:51.760 --> 00:05:56.980
You enter a witness state, where you actually go
beyond your thoughts, because you're

00:05:56.980 --> 00:06:01.820
no longer thinking and you're no longer having
your emotions but you see them from a

00:06:01.820 --> 00:06:04.080
stepping-back witness state.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:08.320
We call it in psychology a meta-cognitive awareness,
where you're beyond your thoughts.

00:06:08.700 --> 00:06:10.460
And you can observe them.

00:06:10.460 --> 00:06:15.780
And that's, I think, the most important thing
