00:06:15.780 --> 00:06:19.860
and, if you remember, Buddha went out to find
meditation because he realised that

00:06:19.860 --> 00:06:22.220
there is a lot of suffering in the world.

00:06:22.220 --> 00:06:23.760
And how do you deal with the suffering?

00:06:23.760 --> 00:06:25.500
You cannot control the life events.

00:06:25.500 --> 00:06:29.840
We all have negative life events, you know: 
your parents are going to die eventually,

00:06:29.840 --> 00:06:33.620
people you love may die, you might have
a divorce, whatever happens to you,

00:06:33.620 --> 00:06:36.560
you cannot really control those life events.

00:06:36.560 --> 00:06:42.700
But what you can control is how you actually
deal with those life events and how you perceive them.

00:06:42.700 --> 00:06:44.960
You can control your state of mind.

00:06:44.960 --> 00:06:46.040
And your thoughts and your emotions.

00:06:46.040 --> 00:06:48.880
And that we do by meditation
